WEBVTT

00:04.587 --> 00:07.868
_

00:07.891 --> 00:11.867
<font color="#fff00">Synced by Bakugan</font>

00:11.971 --> 00:15.099
AARON MAHNKE: On the evening
of February 5, 1921...

00:16.642 --> 00:18.060
Thomas Bradford,

00:18.102 --> 00:19.979
an engineer and psychic,

00:20.020 --> 00:23.524
completed a book about the afterlife.

00:23.566 --> 00:25.860
Then he tested it.

00:29.363 --> 00:32.992
Weeks before, Bradford
had placed an advertisement

00:33.033 --> 00:34.785
in a Detroit newspaper.

00:34.827 --> 00:36.370
He was seeking someone

00:36.412 --> 00:38.789
interested in spiritualistic science.

00:40.332 --> 00:42.418
Ruth Duran, a 40-year-old woman

00:42.460 --> 00:44.879
from one of Detroit's oldest families,

00:44.920 --> 00:47.214
answered Bradford's ad.

00:47.256 --> 00:50.217
She did it out of simple curiosity.

00:50.259 --> 00:52.511
The plan was as straightforward

00:52.553 --> 00:54.180
as it was unsettling.

00:54.221 --> 00:56.140
He would attempt to speak to Ruth

00:56.182 --> 00:57.475
from the other side.

00:57.516 --> 00:59.602
[TYPING]

01:04.565 --> 01:07.193
After Ruth left for the final time,

01:07.234 --> 01:09.779
Thomas locked his boarding house door...

01:12.198 --> 01:13.532
and sealed the room.

01:16.577 --> 01:19.121
Then he blew out the pilot light

01:19.163 --> 01:21.665
and turned on the gas...

01:21.707 --> 01:23.375
[GAS HISSING]

01:23.417 --> 01:27.087
and began what he called
"The Great Adventure."

01:34.637 --> 01:36.639
After his body was discovered,

01:36.680 --> 01:38.808
Ruth told a reporter,

01:38.849 --> 01:42.061
"I believe he will make
his presence known to me."

01:42.102 --> 01:46.565
A week later, she said he spoke.

01:46.607 --> 01:49.610
"I have not traveled
far," the voice said.

01:49.652 --> 01:52.780
"One feels full of
rapture and happiness."

01:54.156 --> 01:56.408
What did Ruth actually hear?

01:56.450 --> 01:58.911
Well, we'll never know for sure.

01:58.953 --> 02:01.956
She took that secret to her own grave.

02:04.041 --> 02:07.962
I'm Aaron Mahnke, and this is Lore.

